{
  "stem": "1169.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "In Linz, they asked everyone to get off, and they took us into the city, or the outskirts of the city somewhere.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They said we have to have a shower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And this was our first face-to-face meeting with the realities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "This shower in Linz was actually a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a shower, but you could-- it was a gas chamber, but you could also take a shower.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We knew it was a gas chamber because we saw cases of poison gas clearly, with the crossed bones that it can kill you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they said that first the woman will take the showers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And prior to taking showers, it seems they shaved every lady.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And there was a tremendous screaming emanating from this building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And the man there told me, listen, you are a boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Nothing will happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Run over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "See what's happening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "The men were very upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I ran over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I saw that everyone is being shaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And a German soldier saw me and gave me-- the first time I got a very painful hit with a rifle butt on my back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then we went to take the showers, the men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "What I remember was, hurtful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They disinfected us, and that solution itched and burned a lot, but it was a very burning solution.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we took the showers and went back to our train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These trains were guarded by Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The overall treatment was not bad, was not bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were treated, I would say-- I mean, at that time we thought it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the context of the situation, they treated us with deference.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this trip from Budapest to Bergen-Belsen took over a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
